### Generating Models

Use the AAPI CLI to generate new models:

```bash
aapi generate model User
aapi generate model Post
```

This will create:
- Mongoose model (`src/models/User.js`)
- GraphQL schema (`src/graphql/typeDefs/User.graphql`)
- GraphQL resolver (`src/graphql/resolvers/UserResolver.js`)

### List Models

To see all generated models in your project:

```bash
aapi list
```

